					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13149811#post-4549205</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13149811/scp-5477#post-4549205</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2020 18:17:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>stormbreath</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3075960</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The security theatre at the start of this is intended to handwave away information about 5477-1, which wasn't important to the story and I didn't want to spend time writing (given the time constraints).</p> <p>In hindsight, it's very much overdone, and I could've gotten the same results done with a simple <strong><tt>[REDACTED CLEARANCE 5477/4]</tt></strong>, rather than everything that I have. I'll be making a change of some sort to remove it or tone it down after the contest wraps up.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13149811#post-4548747</guid>
