				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2020 13:48:46 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ModernMajorGeneral</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>274283</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The gay monsterfucker scp pitch is entertaining, but I'm not sure what the point is of all the blue/purple/red separations and the red redacted text. It's possible I'm missing something, and this is related to the prompt in some way, but it seems that the 'more than meets the eye' aspect is only the relationship between 4444 and 5477-2, in which case the presence of SCP-5477-1 and redacting any information about it is a pretty clunky and inelegant way to get to the point of the article.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
